data.description:
***Seller is offering $6,000 in Concessions with an acceptable offer. New listing on the golf course!!!! Welcome to 572 Westfield Dr in the highly sought-after subdivision of Patrick Farms. This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts an open floor plan with beautiful vinyl flooring and granite countertops throughout. 
The living room is highlighted with a brick fireplace that will be great for staying cozy in the months to come. The kitchen overlooks the living room, which means you can entertain while still making a home-cooked meal for your guests. The master bedroom offers a tremendous amount of space for furniture. The master bath has a freestanding shower, soaking tub, and a double vanity. As you leave the bathroom, you will notice the master closet, which also connects to the laundry room. In the spacious laundry room, you will notice the sink, hanging rack, and plenty of cabinet space. The house also features a back porch that overlooks the 17th hole on the golf course. Call your favorite agent today to schedule your private showing.
